      "review_summary": "The PR preserves bundled capability plugin `manifest.contracts` on synthesized plugin records, seeds contract-backed provider id lists, dedupes runtime-captured ids, and adds focused regression coverage.\n\nPR surface: Source +51, Tests +20. Total +71 across 3 files.\n\nReproducibility: yes. Source inspection shows current bundled records are built without `contracts`, while the same runtime validates captured tools against `record.contracts`; a Feishu manifest declares those tools, so the failure path is source-reproducible.",
